        - Goal: Provide a complete admin panel demo with dev mode protection.
        - Viz/Presentation Method: 
            - Developer Login: Simple form before accessing developer tools.
            - Admin Panel: All subsections (Dashboard, Orders, Products, Customers, Reports, Settings) have their initial HTML structure in place and are managed by JS for dynamic content.
        - Interaction: Admin login, dev login, tab navigation, CRUD operations, order status changes, filter application, dynamic style changes.
        - Justification: Offers a comprehensive and secure (simulated) demo of admin and developer functionalities.
        - Library/Method: Vanilla JavaScript, Tailwind CSS, Chart.js, Fetch API for Gemini.
    -->
